All done. Here's a summary of what was built:

**Files created:**
- `src/claim-office.ts` — Domain logic with `processScenario()` function implementing quote and claim operations
- `src/claim-office.spec.ts` — 40 unit tests covering base premiums, component blocks, premium modifiers, claim processing, cap exhaustion, rounding, and edge cases
- `src/cli.ts` — CLI entry point reading JSON from stdin, writing results to stdout
