- `experiment-done.txt` — Done marker

**All 45 tests pass.** The implementation covers:
- Item base premiums (sword/amulet/staff/potion) and component pricing (rune/moonstone with block discounts)
- Item-specific surcharges (cursed 50%, high enchantment 30%) applied to item base premium
- Policy-wide modifiers (loyalty 20%, first insurance 10%, follow-up 15%) applied to policy base premium sum
- 5G processing fee added last
- Claim deductible (100G per damage), cap (2× insurance sum), high enchantment 50% reimbursement, dragon material full reimbursement
- Rounding in MHPCO's favor (premiums up, payouts down)
- Error handling for unknown types, negative amounts, and mismatched damages
